00:08:30.120 --> 00:08:33.940
where they just put the electricity cables up and make it a West London Trolleybus instead.

00:08:34.380 --> 00:08:36.640
Personally, I think that would have been a brilliant idea.

00:08:36.640 --> 00:08:40.240
A trolleybus is the best of both worlds: Cheaper and easier to build than a tram

00:08:40.240 --> 00:08:42.660
but it still replaces noisy polluting buses.

00:08:43.120 --> 00:08:46.240
In fact, come to think of it, why don't we do that everywhere?

00:08:46.680 --> 00:08:50.340
London's more than 8,000 buses are a huge source of dangerous pollutey air that kills

00:08:50.340 --> 00:08:52.580
that kills 9,500 people per year.

00:08:53.220 --> 00:08:56.360
TfL have tried to make them greener, but the best they've been able to come up with

00:08:56.360 --> 00:08:59.640
